Package inra.ijpb.label.select

Interface RelationalOperator

public interface RelationalOperator
Implementation of a relational operator that computes a boolean value from two scalar input values. Declare abstract methods for integer and floating-point comparisons. Common relational operators are provided as static constants.
Author:
dlegland
